Worklog Timer is a simple Chrome extension that syncs with the Worklog App, making it easy to track your work hours directly from your browser. Start and stop timers with one click to keep your tasks organized and stay on top of your productivity. Perfect for anyone looking to manage time efficiently and log hours seamlessly.

Updates:
Delete log
Edit start and end time
Bug fixes
